 |pages=137–141
 |isbn=978-1-921410-19-2
 |publisher=[[UNSW Press]]
 |ref=harv
}}</ref> As a result, it has become one of the liveliest areas in the discourse between [[Relationship between religion and science|science and religion]].<ref name="Cambridge - Theological Implications">
